rts presents an exhibition of work by young artists who are graduation from their BA Fine Art degree. This year the annual exhibition will feature 33 artists that work in a variety of mediums such as performance, photography, drawing, painting, sculpture and installation. The exhibition looks to give the artists recognition after working at their practice in an academic space. Details: The exhibition takes place until February 1 at the Wits Art Museum, Corner Jorissen Street & Jan Smuts Avenue, Braamfontein. For more information visit www.wits.ac.za/wam/ or call 011 717 1000